data.description: In the heart of Historic Marshall, Mi you will find this charming 3 bedroom plus home office, home that has been newly renovated in the past 5 years. Sit on your front porch or relax on the new deck & entertain. Inside you'll find lots of character with a beam ceiling & reclaimed wood built-in wall shelving unit in the living room. A main floor bedroom or office, formal dining room and a newly remodeled kitchen with portable dishwasher & large main floor Laundry/Mud room with freezer. Three bedrooms upstairs.  Newer windows, freshly painted, hardwood floors, paved driveway, a play house fort in the fenced backyard with remote gate. Enjoy gardening? Space saving garden boxes are ready for spring planting. Carriage barn ready to be transformed. Walk to parks, restaurants , & farmers market.
